dshire, England":"英國奧可福爾諾斯 韋斯頓","Frankley, Worcestershire, England":"英國武斯特斯爾福藍可利","lifeSummary":"當Maud Quartermain於1379年出生在英國奧可福爾諾斯 韋斯頓時，她的父親Richard Quartermain II27歲，母親Joan Grey15歲。她於1394年與Thomas Littleton在英國英格蘭武斯特斯爾結婚。他們至少是1個女兒的父母。她去世於1421年在英國武斯特斯爾伍斯特享年42歲，埋葬在英國武斯特斯爾伍斯特。"},"zh-hans":{"1379–1421":"1379年–1421年","1357–1422":"1357年–1422年","1395–1483":"1395年–1483年","1353–Male":"1353年–殁","1365–Female":"1365年–殁","1379":"1379年","1357":"1357年","1422":"1422年","1421":"1421年","1365":"1365年","1353":"1353年","1483":"1483年","1395":"1395年","1394":"1394年","about 1421":"大约1421年","1382":"1382年","about 1395":"大约1395年","Worcestershire, England":"英国英格兰武斯特斯爾","Worcester, Worcestershire, England":"英国武斯特斯爾伍斯特","North Weston, Oxfordshire, England":"英国奧可福爾諾斯 韋斯頓","Frankley, Worcestershire, England":"英国武斯特斯爾福藍可利","lifeSummary":"当Maud Quartermain于1379年出生在英国奧可福爾諾斯 韋斯頓时，她的父亲Richard Quartermain II27岁，母亲Joan Grey15岁。她于1394年与Thomas Littleton在英国英格兰武斯特斯爾结婚。他们至少是1个女儿的父母。她去世于1421年在英国武斯特斯爾伍斯特享年42岁，埋葬在英国武斯特斯爾伍斯特。"},"hr":{"1379–1421":"1379.–1421.","1357–1422":"1357–1422","1395–1483":"1395–1483","1353–Male":"1353–preminuo","1365–Female":"1365–preminula","1379":"1379.","1357":"1357","1422":"1422","1421":"1421.","1365":"1365","1353":"1353","1483":"1483","1395":"1395","1394":"1394.","about 1421":"oko 1421.","1382":"1382","about 1395":"oko 1395.","Worcestershire, England":"Worcestershire, Engleska, United Kingdom","Worcester, Worcestershire, England":"Worcester, Worcestershire, England","North Weston, Oxfordshire, England":"North Weston, Oxfordshire, England","Frankley, Worcestershire, England":"Frankley, Worcestershire, England"},"cs":{"1379–1421":"1379–1421","1357–1422":"1357–1422","1395–1483":"1395–1483","1353–Male":"1353–Zesnulý","1365–Female":"1365–Zesnulá","1379":"1379","1357":"1357","1422":"1422","1421":"1421","1365":"1365","1353":"1353","1483":"1483","1395":"1395","1394":"1394","about 1421":"okolo 1421","1382":"1382","about 1395":"okolo 1395","Worcestershire, England":"Worcestershire, Anglie, United Ki